REPEL
By default, all instances of repl.REPLServer use an evaluation function that evaluates JavaScript expressions and provides access to Node.js built-in modules. 

File based module
use export to all the functions in different file.

previosly;
// const square={
//   area:(a)=>(a*a),
//   perimeter:(a)=>(4*a)
// }

after;
exports.area = (a) => (a * a);
exports.perimeter = (a) => (4 * a);

